Package: countr
Title: Count Values by Group
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicola", "Rammell", , "nicolarammell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convenience functions to make generating summary tables more efficient. 
    Presently, this package contains a function to count missing values in columns by
    group, outputting a summary tibble of NA value counts. 
